timestamp=2026-07-14T02:05:27.965Z level=INFO run=18ee9f84 message=evaluated permission=bash pattern="python - <<'PY'\nfrom gridcalc import Sheet\ns = Sheet()\n# 256 formula cells ending at V10 with A1 as a formula literal.\nfor i in range(1, 257):\n    col_idx = (i - 1) % 26\n    row_idx = (i - 1) // 26 + 1\n    addr = f\"{chr(65 + col_idx)}{row_idx}\"\n    if i == 1:\n        s.set(addr, \"=1\")\n    else:\n        prev_col_idx = (i - 2) % 26\n        prev_row_idx = (i - 2) // 26 + 1\n        prev_addr = f\"{chr(65 + prev_col_idx)}{prev_row_idx}\"\n        s.set(addr, f\"={prev_addr}+1\")\nprint(s.get(\"V10\"))\nPY" action.permission=* action.action=allow action.pattern=*
